  .container.section
    h2.text-white.text-center U-Hoop Pro Tour Package 
    img(src="/assets/divider-xx-red.png" class="divider")
    p.text-secondary The purpose of a U-Hoops tour team is to give you exposure to our oversea connections while getting a deal. The tours give you an opportunity to play at a professional level and connect straight to scoutes while keeping your skills sharp. 
    p.text-secondary Included:
    ul.text-secondary
      li Hotel stay - shared room
      li 2 Practices Per Day with Professional Coaches
      li 3-4 Games
      li Game Film for all games, posted on the U-Hoop YouTube channel
      li U-Hoops T-Shirt, U-hoops Jersey
      li Introduction to Coaches, Agents, and Scouts
      li Education about that countries basketball market, agents, and contracts
    p.text-secondary Not Included:
    ul.text-secondary 
      li Flight (driver available upon request) U-Hoop has a discount with airlines via 
        a(href="https://www.kiwi.com/us/" target="_blank" class="text-white") kiwi.com
      li Travelers insurance
    p.text-secondary Cost: $600 (may vary slightly by country)

  .container.text-center.divider.sm-container
    a(class="link" href="https://www.facebook.com/UHoopsDotCom/" target="_blank")
      i(class="fab fa-facebook fa-3x icon sm")
    a(class="link" href="https://twitter.com/UHOOPSDOTCOM" target="_blank" class="left-space")
      i(class="fab fa-twitter-square fa-3x icon sm")
  footer.container-fluid
    .row.text-secondary
        p.space &copy; 2018
        p.side-bars.space U-HOOP L.L.C
        p.left-space All Rights Reserved

  div(class="modal fade" id="register" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalCenterTitle" aria-hidden="true")
    div(class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered " role="document")
      div(class="modal-content")
        div(class="modal-header bg-dark")
          h5(class="modal-title text-white" id="exampleModalLongTitle") Register
          button(type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close")
            span(class="text-white" aria-hidden="true") &times;
        div(class="modal-body") 
          div(class="form-group")
            label(for="name" class="col-form-label") Name
            input(type="text" class="form-control" id="name")
          div(class="form-group")
            label(for="email" clas="col-form-label") Email
            input(type="email" class="form-control" id="email")
          div(class="form-group")
            label(for="password" class="col-form-label") Password
            input(type="password" class="form-control" id="password")
          div(class="form-group")
            label(for="confirmPassword" class="col-form-label") Confirm Password
            input(type="password" class="form-control" id="confirmPassword")
        div(class="modal-footer")
          button(type="button" class="btn btn-primary") Create Account 

  div(class="modal fade" id="login" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalCenterTitle" aria-hidden="true")
    div(class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered " role="document")
      div(class="modal-content")
        div(class="modal-header bg-dark")
          h5(class="modal-title text-white" id="exampleModalLongTitle") Login
          button(type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close")
            span(class="text-white" aria-hidden="true") &times;
        div(class="modal-body") 
          div(class="form-group")
            label(for="email-login" clas="col-form-label") Email
            input(type="email" class="form-control" id="email-login")
          div(class="form-group")
            label(for="password-login" class="col-form-label") Password
            input(type="password" class="form-control" id="password-login")
        div(class="modal-footer")
          button(type="button" class="btn btn-primary") Login 
